prod.desciption:
Jordan Brand revisited a colorway from their Player Exclusive archive for the Air Jordan 6 Electric Green. The Electric Green is nearly identical to the Air Jordan 6 Oregon Ducks PE that surfaced in 2018.

The Air Jordan 6 Electric Green features an all-black Durabuck upper with hits of Electric Green on the heel tab, tongue, and midsole. A milky, green translucent outsole finishes off this retro model.

The Air Jordan 6 Electric Green released in June of 2021 and retailed for $190.
